						<div class="postbody">For completeness:
<br />
<br />Have player leave his NES on between runs.
<br />
<br />Have player record his items and position, and enter them directly (honor system).
<br />
<br />Use a <a href="http://para.maxim-ic.com/en/search.mvp?fam=memory&amp;489=NV%20SRAM&amp;232=Yes&amp;tree=memory" class="postlink">NVSRAM with internal battery</a>, in a normal WRAM-supporting board.</div>

